snippet.title: 𝐏𝐄𝐍𝐔𝐌𝐁𝐑𝐀 𝐋𝐀𝐍𝐄 (𝐃𝐞𝐦𝐨 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐫)
snippet.description:
Penumbra Lane is a short, point-and-click horror adventure in which you, a cat-man named Xavier, must break your lease at Penumbra Lane, by collecting keys, solving puzzles, and avoiding death. 

Demo will be releasing on Itch.io and Steam,
Late December 2022. :) 

The remainder of the game is slated to arrive mid 2023!
Follow me here for more: https://twitter.com/HazeyEyed
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Happy Halloween! :3
